videos.description: NC State's Ricky Person Jr. scores a touchdown from the 1-yard line for his first career score.
videos.headline: Person scores first TD for NC State

videos.description: Ryan Finley pass is pulled down by Kelvin Harmon for the 8-yard NC State touchdown.
videos.headline: Finley finds Harmon for 8-yard NC State TD

videos.description: NC State defensive lineman Larrell Murchison leaps to snag the interception in FSU territory.
videos.headline: NC State D-lineman snags INT

videos.description: NC State runs the option to Ricky Person Jr. who sneaks into the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: NC State's Person sneaks in for TD

videos.description: James Blackman throws a dart to Cam Akers for an 8-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Blackman connects with Akers for 8-yard FSU TD

videos.description: Ryan Finley throws a 2-yard dart to Jakobi Meyers who stretches out for the NC State touchdown.
videos.headline: Finley throws 2-yard dart for NC State TD

videos.description: Tamorrion Terry makes a sweet 37-yard catch while falling out of bounds over a FSU defender.
videos.headline: NC State's Terry makes big-time catch falling out of bounds

videos.description: James Blackman finds Tamorrion Terry in the back of the end zone for a 10-yard FSU touchdown.
videos.headline: Blackman connects with Terry for 10-yard TD pass

videos.description: NC State's Ryan Finley floats a 2-yard pass out to Ricky Person Jr. for the touchdown, putting the Wolfpack on top of the Seminoles 44-21.
videos.headline: Finley throws floater to Person Jr. for NC State TD
